<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Receipt Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #2d3436; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #f0f4f0; }
      .container { background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.1); }
      .header-bar { height: 6px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2d6a4f, #52b788, #f4a261); }
      .header { text-align: center; padding: 28px 28px 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #52b788; }
      .header .icon { font-size: 48px; color: #52b788; }
      h2 { color: #1b4332; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 20px; }
      .body { padding: 28px; }
      .greeting { font-size: 17px; color: #2d3436; margin-bottom: 14px; }
      .body-text { color: #555; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr; gap: 12px; margin: 20px 0; background: #f8faf8; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #d8e8d8; }
      .label { font-weight: 700; color: #2d6a4f; font-size: 13px; }
      .value { color: #2d3436; }
      .message { background: #f0f4f0; padding: 16px; border-left: 4px solid #52b788; margin: 20px 0; white-space: pre-wrap; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
      .message-title { font-weight: 700; color: #2d6a4f; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; }
      .next-steps { background: #e8f5e9; border: 1px solid #a5d6a7; color: #1b5e20; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .next-steps h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #2d6a4f; font-size: 15px; }
      .next-steps ul { margin: 8px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
      .next-steps li { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px; }
      .contact-info { background: #fff8f0; border-left: 4px solid #f4a261; padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; color: #6b4226; font-size: 14px; }
      .signature { margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 18px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; color: #555; }
      .signature strong { color: #2d6a4f; }
      .footer { text-align: center; color: #95a5a6; font-size: 11px; padding: 18px; border-top: 2px dashed #d8e8d8; }
      .footer p { margin: 3px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-bar"></div>
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon">✓</div>
        <h2>Receipt Confirmation</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</div>
        <p class="body-text">
          We confirm that we have received your message. It has been recorded
          and our team will process it as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="label">Reference:</div>
          <div class="value">REF-{{timestamp}}</div>
          <div class="label">Subject:</div>
          <div class="value">{{subject}}</div>
          <div class="label">Date Received:</div>
          <div class="value">{{timestamp}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
          <div class="message-title">Your Message Summary:</div>
          {{message}}
        </div>
        <div class="next-steps">
          <h3>Next Steps</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Your message has been forwarded to the relevant team</li>
            <li>You will receive a detailed response within 24–48 hours</li>
            <li>For urgent matters, please don't hesitate to contact us again</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <strong>Need Urgent Help?</strong><br />
          If your request requires immediate attention, feel free to contact us again
          and specify the urgent nature of your request.
        </div>
        <div class="signature">
          <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The {{companyName}} Team</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This confirmation email was generated automatically.</p>
        <p>Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
